<h1 id="sponsorship">Support</h1>

<p><span>
MicroBlocks is a not-for-profit project under the fiscal sponsorship of the
<a href="https://sfconservancy.org" target="_blank">Software Freedom Conservancy</a>,
a 501(c)(3) non-profit.
</span></p>

<ul class="flex"><li><a href="http://sfconservancy.org" target="_blank"><img class="logo" src="sfc.png"/></a></li></ul>

<p><span>
MicroBlocks can accept tax-deductible donations, grants, and sponsorships
from individuals and organizations.
If you find MicroBlocks useful, we invite you or your organization to contribute.
</span></p>

<p><span>
You can use the Donate button at the bottom of the page or click
<a onclick="document.querySelector('.donate.desktop form').submit()">here</a>
to make a small personal donation to the project via PayPal or credit card.
</span></p>

<p><span>
If you would like to make a larger donation via wire transfer
or sponsor this project in some other way, please contact the Software Freedom Conservancy at
<a href="mailto:supporters@tix.sfconservancy.org">supporters@tix.sfconservancy.org</a>.
Be sure to mention that you want your donation to go to the MicroBlocks project.
</span></p>

<p><span>Thank you. Every little bit helps!</span></p>
